  "knowledge_nodes": [
    {
      "content": "下落的速率是否真正取决于物体的重量？ 如果\"重者下落更快\"只是空气阻力造成的表象，那么在思想实验、 控制条件实验以及真空极限下，应当分别看到怎样的结果？",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "question",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_38a2b644cfad2eba",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "main_question",
          "module": "motivation",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "0.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "想象一个重球 H 和一个轻球 L 从同一高度落下。 先分别考虑它们各自的\"自然下落速度\"，再考虑把二者用细绳绑成 复合体 HL 后一起下落，会得到什么结果。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "setting",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_628c2161ea1c791a",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "thought_experiment_env",
          "module": "setting",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "0.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "一个理想化的无空气阻力环境， 只保留重力作用，不让介质阻力参与落体过程。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "setting",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_ee680320e27c6706",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "vacuum_env",
          "module": "setting",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "0.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "重的物体比轻的物体下落得更快。 下落速度与重量成正比。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_1d4e35187298d4af",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "heavier_falls_faster",
          "module": "aristotle",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "0.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "在日常空气环境中，从同一高度落下时，石头通常比羽毛更早落地； 重物看起来往往比轻物下落得更快。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_ab18097122aca931",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "everyday_observation",
          "module": "aristotle",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "0.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "日常经验反复呈现\"重物先落地、轻物后落地\"的现象， 如果不区分空气阻力等外在因素，人们很自然会把这种表象 归纳成一条普遍规律：重量越大，下落越快。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_3d2e36ffc0f3d068",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "inductive_step",
          "module": "aristotle",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "0.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "在水、油、空气等不同介质中比较轻重物体的下落， 会发现介质越稠密，速度差异越明显；介质越稀薄，差异越不明显。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_1812972de3fd34dd",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "medium_density_observation",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "0.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "伽利略的斜面实验把下落过程放慢到可测量尺度后显示： 不同重量的小球在相同斜面条件下呈现近似一致的加速趋势， 与\"重量越大速度越大\"的简单比例律并不相符。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_183a7fccf36f78f4",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "inclined_plane_observation",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "0.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "在思想实验环境中暂时接受亚里士多德定律： 轻球天然比重球下落更慢。于是当轻球与重球绑在一起时， 轻球应当拖慢重球，复合体 HL 的下落速度应慢于单独的重球 H。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_2ff573a041ede2f7",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "tied_pair_slower",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "0.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "按照\"重量越大，下落越快\"的同一条定律， 被绑在一起后的复合体 HL 总重量大于单独的重球 H， 因而它又应当比 H 下落更快。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_6e5e00cf193c7fb2",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "tied_pair_faster",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "0.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "同一定律对同一绑球系统同时预测\"更慢\"和\"更快\"，自相矛盾。 亚里士多德落体定律因绑球矛盾而不能成立。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "contradiction",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_1eb3a3d24b17ae79",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "tied_balls_contradiction",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "0.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "如果从水到空气，随着介质变稀薄，轻重物体的速度差异持续缩小， 那么这种差异更像是外部阻力效应，而不是重量本身对自由落体速度的直接支配。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_36305fff24c18cd7",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "medium_difference_shrinks",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "0.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "由此可知，日常观察到的速度差异更应被解释为介质阻力造成的表象， 而不是重量本身决定自由落体速度的证据。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_30a2261ddef7283b",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "air_resistance_is_confound",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "0.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "斜面实验把自由落体减慢到可测量尺度后， 显示不同重量的小球获得近似一致的加速趋势， 支持\"重量不是决定落体快慢的首要因素\"。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_c5f7c88a430d6d84",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "inclined_plane_supports_equal_fall",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "0.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "综合以上三条线索：绑球矛盾推翻旧定律、介质分析排除干扰因素、 斜面实验提供正面支持——在真空中， 不同重量的物体应以相同速率下落。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_a73ca9fdf3ef6242",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "vacuum_prediction",
          "module": "reasoning",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "0.0.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "能否在足够接近真空的条件下直接比较重球与轻球的下落时间？ 如果日常差异确实来自空气阻力，那么真正决定性的实验应当在 几乎无介质的环境中完成。",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "question",
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "raw_node_id": "raw_dc1761660a7974e8",
      "source_refs": [
        {
          "knowledge_name": "follow_up_question",
          "module": "follow_up",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "0.0.0"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
